text: Pamela Rooke (23 June 1955 â€“ 3 April 2022), also known as Jordan and Jordan Mooney, was an English model and actress. She was known her work with Vivienne Westwood and the Sex boutique in the Kings Road area of London in the mid-1970s. She was seen as an icon of the London punk subculture. Rooke was born in Seaford, East Sussex. Rooke died on 3 April 2022 in London, England from bile duct cancer, aged 66. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Models from London Category:Artists from London Category:Actors from London Category:Deaths from cholangiocarcinoma Category:People from East Sussex
